name: The Press Project @ The Hard Rock Cafe - October 2nd, 2010
description:
*TIX ARE NO LONGER AVAILABLE ONLINE.  PLENTY WILL BE FOR SALE AT THE DOOR*  THANKS AND SEE YOU THERE!!!

Come see a rare Boston area performance of The Press Project w/ the original keyboard and Moog stylings of Dan Shure and the lyrical barrage of B. Cap and The Face of Fate.  You do not want to miss this show because they don't play many.

This is one your grandkids will be telling their grandkids about.  2.5 hours of Press Project hip-hop, funk, jazz, soul and rock n' roll.  Let your mind take a break and your body do the movin' and & shakin.'
